### AI Resume Grader - API Test File
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or JetBrains HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔍 Health Check
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### GET Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔐 Auth Routes  (/api/auth)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###

### Login
# Copy the token from the response and paste it into @token above
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# 📄 Analysis Routes  (/api/analysis)
# All routes below require Authorization header
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Upload Resume (multipart/form-data)
# Replace <path-to-your-resume.pdf> with an actual file path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analysis/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resume"; filename="resume.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< C:\path\to\your\resume.pdf
------FormBoundary--

###

### Analyze Resume (after uploading)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analysis/analyze
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resumeId": "PASTE_RESUME_ID_HERE",
  "jobDescription": "We are looking for a full-stack developer with experience in React, Node.js, and MongoDB."
}

###

### Rewrite Resume
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analysis/rewrite-resume
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resumeId": "PASTE_RESUME_ID_HERE",
  "jobDescription": "We are looking for a full-stack developer with experience in React, Node.js, and MongoDB."
}

###

### Generate Interview Questions
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analysis/interview-questions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resumeId": "PASTE_RESUME_ID_HERE",
  "jobDescription": "We are looking for a full-stack developer with experience in React, Node.js, and MongoDB."
}

###

### Get Analysis History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analysis/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Delete an Analysis by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/analysis/PASTE_ANALYSIS_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
